{"id":232869606,"title":"髮型照片可以互相利用嗎？？？","content":"我去年在桃園某間美髮店燙頭髮，當時我就有說不要放正面照，後來髮型師還是上傳了正面跟背面的照片😣\n(題外：明明沒染過，只是天生咖啡色，還標明染燙，還取了髮色的名字😑)\n\n原本想說算了🙄...\n\n結果今天突然看到(同一間店)另一名設計師，她的貼文裡面竟然有放我的髮型正面照片！？🤔\n請問這樣互用照片是可以的嗎？\n==================================\n更：剛剛去看另一名設計師的ig\nhttps://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIm.jpg\n竟然說是她的作品！？\n==================================\n我的設計師說會請她刪除，她說她們的照片是通用的。\n我覺得不太ok，這樣不是欺騙消費者嗎？如果哪天我說要這個髮型，只是其實這是另一個設計師的作品，那妳真的能做出一模一樣的髮型嗎?\n我的設計師說這部分他們會改進，希望真的會改進😶\n只是我暫時不會去那間了😥😥","excerpt":"我去年在桃園某間美髮店燙頭髮，當時我就有說不要放正面照，後來髮型師還是上傳了正面跟背面的照片，（題外：明明沒染過，只是天生咖啡色，還標明染燙，還取了髮色的名字），原本想說算了...，結果今天突然看到（","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"62268850-d2b4-4c21-a7a3-26e71702a276","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-11T06:35:22.537Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-11T11:25:48.961Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":29,"tags":[],"topics":["照片","髮型","問題","求解"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美髮","forumAlias":"hairsalon","school":"元智大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":29}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIm.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"ada8a2e6-fa13-4090-81fd-493f893e4bab","url":"https://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIml.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIml.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIml.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-11T10:44:53.698Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-11T11:25:48.961Z"},{"id":"ada8a2e6-fa13-4090-81fd-493f893e4bab","url":"https://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIm.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/9fDmuIm","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/9fDmuIml.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-11T10:44:53.698Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-11T11:25:48.961Z"}],"postAvatar